  "description": "Align Social Media Icons to Right Side of Page Header\n\nReposition the social media icons in the page header from their current left-aligned position to right-aligned, improving visual balance and layout consistency.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate social media icons container in the header/top section of the page\n- Update CSS/styling to align icons to the right side of the page\n- Ensure proper spacing from the right edge of the page/container\n- Maintain consistent vertical alignment with other header elements\n- Verify responsive behavior on mobile, tablet, and desktop screen sizes\n- Test that icons remain clickable and accessible after repositioning\n- Ensure no overlap with other header content (logo, navigation, etc.)",
